A User will recieve a Notification if he/she gets a new Follower
A User will recieve a Notification if a User Likes his/her Post
A User will recieve a Notification if a User Likes his/her Comment
A User will receive a Notification if a User Comments on his/her Post
A User will receive a Notification if that User is Mentioned in a Post
A User will receive a Notification if that User is Mentioned in a Comment
A User will receive a Notification if his/her Post is Shared by another User
